metadata.description:
Get a PASS to the world of the fine art at the NFT space. 
The 10k collection pass is confirming your unconditional right to easily become a collector of fine art by contemporary artists. 

NFA.space aims to become the Worldwide Web 3.0 collection house based on the principles of equal opportunities for all talented artists from around the world and transparency of authorship based on blockchain technology.
metadata.name: The 10k collection: Pass
